Yes, My Lady.

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:12.130
The Ghost King of Lingbi

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:14.340
was no more after Master's passing.

00:03:14.870 --> 00:03:16.820
Where did this new Ghost King come from?

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:24.220
Could it be...

00:03:28.150 --> 00:03:30.570
Although this is a branch of Lingbi Sect,

00:03:31.030 --> 00:03:31.820
the Ghost King

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.450
is here.

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:35.850
That means this branch is the most prominent.

00:03:36.430 --> 00:03:38.170
You all have joined us as fresh maidservants.

00:03:38.830 --> 00:03:40.580
You all must obey the rules.

00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:41.650
Understood?

00:03:41.790 --> 00:03:42.610
Yes, madam.

00:04:18.550 --> 00:04:19.700
What are you doing here?

00:04:25.990 --> 00:04:27.140
It's all my fault.

00:04:27.190 --> 00:04:28.020
I got lost

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.260
by accident.

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:29.850
Go away!

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:31.290
Yes, madam.

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:39.330
How dare you leave the team without permission?

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:41.500
