Saintess,

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:16.610
we found one of Fenglai Pavilion's bases

00:11:16.630 --> 00:11:18.340
according to the leads on the silver coin.

00:11:18.390 --> 00:11:20.820
But the place was already empty when we got there.

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:22.420
They even set up explosive traps,

00:11:22.440 --> 00:11:24.060
causing us to suffer countless casualties.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:25.650
I managed to survive narrowly.

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:27.460
First, they robbed you guys.

00:11:27.510 --> 00:11:28.850
After that, they gave you guys fake leads

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:31.650
to lure you into the traps they had set up at Fenglai Pavilion.

00:11:31.960 --> 00:11:33.370
This bait-and-switch move

00:11:34.080 --> 00:11:35.370
