00:13:37.870 --> 00:13:38.850
What are you afraid of?

00:13:40.390 --> 00:13:43.010
Xiao Huan wants to abolish the status verification system

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:45.220
so that the people won't need to suffer because of taxes.

00:13:45.910 --> 00:13:48.100
