00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:51.060
As for the Great Qi he wishes to protect,

00:13:53.320 --> 00:13:54.300
I'm going to demolish it,

00:13:55.270 --> 00:13:57.580
bit by bit.

00:14:13.270 --> 00:14:14.180
Xiao Qianqing.

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:16.220
You have to be able to differentiate

00:14:16.240 --> 00:14:17.250
between right and wrong.

00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:18.820
So what if you do ascend the throne?

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:20.370
What do you think people will think about you?

00:14:20.510 --> 00:14:22.300
You'll truly become a villain who usurped the throne by killing your brother!

00:14:22.840 --> 00:14:24.130
Qianqing, do you like the present

00:14:24.510 --> 00:14:25.570
