00:14:33.150 --> 00:14:34.490
you and I

00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:38.250
will cut all ties.

00:14:53.750 --> 00:14:56.220
Your Highness, you didn't attend the morning court session.

00:14:56.630 --> 00:14:58.060
It turns out that you're here,

00:14:58.320 --> 00:14:59.770
fretting over your lost love.

00:15:01.790 --> 00:15:02.700
Preceptor Du,

00:15:03.910 --> 00:15:05.650
you should mind your own business.

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:07.700
I don't mind

00:15:08.630 --> 00:15:10.980
getting another obedient lackey from Nanrong Palace

00:15:11.660 --> 00:15:12.580
and allowing him

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:14.760
to enjoy the fun of being the next Imperial Preceptor.

00:15:18.200 --> 00:15:19.340
I came to find you

00:15:19.870 --> 00:15:21.490
because I have some business

00:15:22.790 --> 00:15:24.580
with you.

00:15:39.270 --> 00:15:40.250
Du Tingxin!

00:15:45.200 --> 00:15:46.610
You think I don't dare to kill you?

00:15:54.480 --> 00:15:56.420
If you capture a bird with a fiery personality,

00:15:57.200 --> 00:15:59.580
there's no way you can trap it in a cage.

00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:02.420
It'll think of everything it can to escape.

00:16:02.550 --> 00:16:04.060
It will only give up after ramming itself to death

00:16:04.360 --> 00:16:05.490
in the cage.

00:16:14.550 --> 00:16:16.180
Your Highness, please be appeased.

